{"tid":1167342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉指德國或遭誤導才批出難民庇護　港府應澄清","createTime":"2019-05-23T03:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T11:01:47.000Z","uid":241764,"like":2,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee40211a3f0e12f90ed1653eacc3388eb51395a","tid":1167342,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"在2016年旺角暴亂案中棄保潛逃的「本土民主前線」成員黃台仰和李東昇，據報去年5月在德國獲得難民庇護。立法會議員葉劉淑儀今(23日)出席電台節目時表示，兩人若返港受審會得到公平審訊，但現時德國給予二人難民庇護身份，反映德認為他們返港後會遭到迫害。葉劉淑儀更指，德國或是被誤導才發出難民庇護。<br />\n<br />\n她認為特區政府應就此事作出反駁，為保障香港法庭的聲譽，港府應向德方澄清二人返港後會有公平審訊。對於有指黃台仰擔憂一旦回港有機會被移交到內地，葉劉淑儀直指說法荒謬，因香港與德國的移交協議訂明，除非得到德國認同，否則被移交人士不會再被移送到其他地區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190523/bkn-20190523101510541-0523_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190523%2Fbkn-20190523101510541-0523_00822_001.html&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1UoyoxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=1c378fcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190523/bkn-20190523101510541-0523_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"12a22d1b88796cf069484fccd5e7ff846f2a47ab","tid":1167342,"uid":8410,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"熱烈慶祝香港出現政治難民, 德國認同香港已等同中國"},{"pid":"5e03acc85bc134da5f7bac1f2068f4b3a7e56a58","tid":1167342,"uid":39200,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:43:39.000Z","msg":"葉劉咁樣似屌柒婆多過屌德國"},{"pid":"2e011fd3f26f8b565bb7d0901f3bd07f6e6e4e63","tid":1167342,"uid":44486,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:44:26.000Z","msg":"jealous <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d86bc5ca826ed06b63cd95eecfd695c04197db","tid":1167342,"uid":50457,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:44:56.000Z","msg":"個頭伸咁出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br 